Review control description: (15) 'Tranche thickness' means the measure calculated as detachment point (D)
minus attachment point (A), where D and A are calculated in accordance with
paragraphs 33 to 37;

Review control description: The amount of PDI in
excess of amount admissible as Tier 1 shall qualify as Tier 2 capital subject to
provisions contained in these Directions;

Review control description: (5) Rate of interest
The interest payable to the investors may be either at a fixed rate or at a floating
rate referenced to a market determined rupee interest benchmark rate;

Review control description: (10) Discount
The PDI instruments shall not be subject to a progressive discount for capital
adequacy purposes since these are perpetual;

Review control description: (14) Grant of advances against PDI
A non-deposit taking NBFC issuing PDI shall not grant advances against the
security of its PDI;

Review control description: (6) DTA created by credit to opening balance of Revenue Reserves or to Profit and
Loss account for the current year shall be included under item 'others' of 'Other
Assets';

Review control description: However, the NBFC shall reduce 50 per cent of the
amount of credit enhancement given from Tier 1 capital and the balance from
Tier 2 capital;

Review control description: (iv) Furthermore, an NBFC shall not use the credit assessments issued by one
external CRA for one or more tranches and those of another external CRA
for other positions (whether retained or purchased)

